  * Support rsvg-2.12.
  * Add RSVG::BUILD_VERSION

Ruby/GtkMozEmbed [NEW]:
  * Merged. [Mirko Maischberber]
  * Add Gtk::MozEmbed::BUILD_VERSION [Masao Mutoh]

== Ruby-GNOME2 0.13.0: 2005-07-31

