    Gda::DataModel, Gda::Provider, Gda::Quarklist, Gda::Connection
  * Renamed, Moved [Laurent Sansonetti]
    * Gda::DataModel#editable? => #updatable?
    * #editing? => changed?
    * #begin_edit => #begin_update
    * #cancel_edit => #cancel_update
    * #end_edit => #end_update

