    * Gtk::HtmlView, Gtk::HtmlStream, extconf.rb

Ruby/GtkGLExt:
  * Added some methods, improved, fixed bugs: [Vincent Isambart, Masao Mutoh]
    * Gdk::GLDrawable, sample/*.rb

